comments: Powell (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Johnson's (TOR) path and does not deliver any contact.
As Doncic (DAL) dribbles off the pick, he brings his arm under Johnson's (TOR) arm and initiates marginal arm contact.
Birch (TOR) draws Porzingis (DAL) into the air and Porziginis makes contact with Birch during his shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Flynn's (TOR) path and does not deliver any contact.
Bembry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Powell's (DAL) backside during the rebound.
Powell (DAL) makes marginal contact with Birch's (TOR) lower body as they both return to the floor during the rebound.
Brunson (DAL) makes contact with the ball then marginal follow-through contact with Flynn's (TOR) hand/wrist during his driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the play overturns the on-court out-of-bounds ruling. Flynn (TOR) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and possession is correctly awarded to DAL.
Doncic (DAL) naturally loses control of his dribble and Flynn (TOR) makes marginal contact with Doncic during the steal.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with Flynn's (TOR) non-shooting hand as he removes it from the ball during his driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Flynn's (TOR) path.
Birch (TOR) legally contests Porzingis' (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Gillespie (TOR) firms up in Brunson's (DAL) path and does not deliver any contact during the pick.
Powell (DAL) makes marginal contact with Gillespie's (TOR) arm as he secures the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact with the ball and dislodges the ball from Gillespie (TOR).

Gillespie (TOR) and Doncic (DAL) make incidental contact with each other during the loose ball.  Toronto attempts to call a timeout but they do not have possession of the ball and a jump ball is correctly called during the tie-up.
Porzingis (DAL) makes contact with Gillespie's (TOR) arm during his shot attempt.
Richardson (DAL) briefly grasps Bembry's (TOR) arm as he makes his move to receive the throw-in but the contact is marginal.
Bembry (TOR) commits a take foul on Richardson (DAL).
Bembry (TOR) commits a take foul on Richardson (DAL).
Powell (DAL) legally contest Flynn's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
Bembry (TOR) commits a take foul on Richardson (DAL).
Finney-Smith (DAL) legally contests Harris' (TOR) jump shot attempt.
